{"iti46:0.1":"Itivuttaka 46 ","iti46:0.2":"Dukanipata ","iti46:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","iti46:0.4":"Sikkhanisamsasutta ","iti46:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti46:2.1":"“Sikkhanisamsa, bhikkhave, viharatha pannuttara vimuttisara satadhipateyya. ","iti46:2.2":"Sikkhanisamsanam, bhikkhave, viharatam pannuttaranam vimuttisaranam satadhipateyyanam dvinnam phalanam annataram phalam patikankham—","iti46:2.3":"dittheva dhamme anna, sati va upadisese anagamita”ti. ","iti46:2.4":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti46:2.5":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti46:3.1":"“Paripunnasikkham apahanadhammam, ","iti46:3.2":"Pannuttaram jatikhayantadassim; ","iti46:3.3":"Tam ve munim antimadehadharim, ","iti46:3.4":"Maranjaham brumi jaraya paragum. ","iti46:4.1":"Tasma sada jhanarata samahita, ","iti46:4.2":"Atapino jatikhayantadassino; ","iti46:4.3":"Maram sasenam abhibhuyya bhikkhavo, ","iti46:4.4":"Bhavatha jatimaranassa paraga”ti. ","iti46:5.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti46:5.2":"Navamam. "}